{"tid":1269794,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃旗定黑旗","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T21:58:29.000Z","uid":190579,"like":37,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d9335cf7707de3b829cc2c312ee67f203a6168c4","tid":1269794,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"請放得自己意見，唔好淨係正/負皮。<br />\n<br />\n理性討論，尊重他人意見，唔好謾罵。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">記住！我哋目標只有一個：就係港共政權！唔係自己人！<br />\n</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑<br />\n<br />\n事源：<br />\n游蕙禎: 請勿在71行升黑旗禮. 黑旗代表恐怖主義<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1269338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1269338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5a344e91069a1a047b3706bf13e044b7ecc2b5e","tid":1269794,"uid":190579,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"我先。<br />\n<br />\n實際作用嚟講，升咩旗分別唔大，最主要都係象徵意義。<br />\n既然係咁，無須執著黑旗。<br />\n黃旗代表自由同希望，<br />\n亦都代表第一個烈士既遺志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以黃旗都可以表達哀傷<br />\n<br />\n黑旗最主要影響外國人觀感。<br />\n黑衣可以，但黑旗唔同。<br />\n你諗下其實歐美近幾年其中一個最關心同貼身既國際大事，就係ISIS 。<br />\n見到支黑旗就會引起潛意識恐懼同厭惡，支黑旗比佢哋騎劫咗。<br />\n<br />\n有巴打話呢個階段已經唔洗計較人地點睇，我認同一半。<br />\n可以換嚟實際效果既事，的確可以優先考慮，大眾睇法其次。但我認為今次黃定黑實際效果上分別唔大，所以應優先考慮大眾睇法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋係正義之師，都要話比人知我地係正義之師</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"9343c80781fc3c37dda0daafbd9fe1ca47cec310","tid":1269794,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"554d375698793b7dcf63ea2592985fbe9e89a2a9","tid":1269794,"uid":155821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"黃"},{"pid":"4f43a7b0e57df9cd6e51ae7e81eb35d4f8a5250a","tid":1269794,"uid":11827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:37:29.000Z","msg":"啱=望向前面發出金黃色嘅曙光 你地每朝清早一樣會感受到陽光"},{"pid":"5c9850bb32e906715249d3e0f05bff0fcf9b0cc5","tid":1269794,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T21:58:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}